<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1018.61033.figure73>
    dc:description "Figure 73. Holotype female Cryptophyllium yapicum comb. nov. photographed by RTC A habitus, dorsal B ventrolateral view of the protibiae showing the unique lobe shape C details of the thorax and head, dorsal D lateral view of the thorax-head E terminalia, ventral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/510537" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1018.61033.figure74>
    dc:description "Figure 74. Three additional non-type specimens of Cryptophyllium yapicum comb. nov., photographs by Miho Maeda, Jerilynn Chun, and James Boone, 2020 (BPBM). Corresponding data labels below the specimen A female habitus, dorsal B associated data labels C female habitus, dorsal D associated data labels E male habitus, dorsal F associated data labels." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/510538" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

